      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely gotta see this beauty! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this car from day one, and it's in spectacular shape inside and out. It drives like a total dream and still has that fresh feel. If you\u2019re looking for something that's been loved and kept in perfect order, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
