    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a definitive example of the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant features individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. The chassis maintains its factory rigidity, supported by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock for optimal lateral dynamics. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and VANOS system validation. With zero subframe deformation and a pristine underbody, this specimen represents the pinnacle of M-division engineering for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
